# Gift API examples

### Get all gifts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/gifts

### Get gift by id
GET http://localhost:8080/api/gifts/{{id}}

### Create a gift
POST http://localhost:8080/api/gifts
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bút chì màu",
  "cost": 150,
  "src": "/product/butchim.webp",
  "quantity": 20
}

### Update a gift
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/gifts/{{id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Bút chì màu (phiên bản mới)",
  "cost": 180,
  "src": "/product/butchim_v2.webp",
  "quantity": 15
}

### Delete a gift
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/gifts/{{id}}

# Quick notes:
# - Use the sample ids returned by POST/GET responses.
# - Endpoints return JSON. POST returns created object, PUT returns updated object, DELETE returns 204 on success.

### Upload an image for a gift (multipart)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/gifts/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data

--file: (select file)

# Response example:
# { "path": "/uploads/product/1699999999999-12345.png", "filename": "1699999999999-12345.png" }
